caption: Table 1: Performance of Algorithm 1 and Algorithm 2 on the MNIST dataset.
description: This table presents the performance comparison of two algorithms (Off-policy Algorithm 1 and On-policy Algorithm 2) on the MNIST dataset.  The performance is evaluated using two metrics: Average Progressive Reward and Test Accuracy.  Each algorithm is tested with two different reward estimators: Binary and Lipschitz. The numbers represent the mean and standard deviation (in parentheses) across multiple runs.
